dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents public lands for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Jefferson_PublicLands_2016.gdb.[This coverage contains polygons for all known park and public lands in Jefferson; including municipal parks.Park Codes:H = HuntingC = Co ParksP = State ParksO = OtherS = School ParkT = Town ParkL = Lake ManagementF = Federal LandMP = Municipal Parks (City or Village)]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
